distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check connects to a Hivemanager NG cloud account and get a list of all connected devices.
 Then the connection state and currently active users will be checked. It is possible to set levels for
 the maximum number of active clients.
 To connect to the Hivemanager NG cloud a special Datasource Program is used. You can find it under the
 name <i>Aerohive HiveManager NG</i> in WATO -> Datasource Programs.

